@artechouse is officially open in Houston and you definitely don’t want to miss out! The exhibit bridges art and tech to take you through time and space. The space also features collaborations with NASA ✨☄️

Hours: 
Daily from 3pm-10pm

Location: 
600 W Sixth St

Tickets are $25 general admission & $15 for children. 

Thank you to @publiccontent & @pcinfluence for inviting me to this experience! 

#thingstodoinhouston #houston #htx #dateideas #technology #immersiveexperience#artexhibition #artechouse

✨HOUSTON’S NEWEST GEM✨@chardonhouston is officially opening its doors February 21st, and trust me, you’re going to want a reservation! Located inside the @thompsonhoustonhotel, this modern French restaurant transports you to Paris and delivers an unforgettable dining experience, perfect for a girls’ night or date night! 🌹

From Wagyu Steak Tartare to Le Grand Macaron Au Chocolat, every bite was DIVINE. Paired with a French 75 or a glass of wine, and you’ve got a night to remember! 🥂

Mark your calendars and get ready to book your table! This is going to be Houston’s go-to French dining spot.

📍Chardon 
1711 Allen Pkwy 
Houston, TX 77019

Here’s what we tried:
✨ Wagyu Steak Tartare
✨ Kaviari Ossetra Caviar
✨ Mussels w/ Fries & Aioli
✨ Wagyu Beef Cheek Bourguignon
✨ Le Grand Macaron Au Chocolat

Thank you to @pcinfluence for hosting me for their exclusive preview!

#houston #houstontexas #houstonfood #houstonfoodblogger
#downtownhouston #explorehouston #houstonhiddengems #texas #texasfood #texasfoodblogger #htx #thingstodoinhouston #houstondatenight

So grateful to have joined the @houstonautoshow for the BMW i Series driving experience! We tried out the i4 and iX and absolutely LOVED both. As an EV owner, after experiencing BMW’s EV models I can definitely say @bmwusa attention to detail is unmatched. 

Now is a great time to look into these models if you’ve been considering switching to an EV because BMW has excellent rebates and offers at most certified dealers nationwide.

If you’re in the Houston area, be sure to visit either the @bmwhoustonnorth or @bmwofwesthouston dealers to try these two models or any other i Series model for yourself!
